Spray nonstick skillet with Market Pantry cooking spray. Season patties with salt and pepper. Cook patties in skillet over medium high heat for 8 to 10 minutes or until internal temperature reaches 165 degrees F. Meanwhile, heat broccoli as package directs. If desired, heat French fried onions as package directs. Place burgers on serving dish. Spoon broccoli mixture over burgers and top with French fried onions.